sections.heading: to 76-14-15 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 2001, ch. 76, § 1, repealed 76-14-1 to 76-14-15 NMSA 1978, enacted by Laws 1927, ch. 164, §§ 1 to 5, Laws 1957, ch. 136, §§ 1 to 7 and 9, and Laws 1977, ch. 116, §§ 1 and 2, relating to cotton ginning and handling, effective July 1, 2001. For provisions of former sections,seethe 2000 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
